  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Draft Environment (Principles and Governance) Bill 2018
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph ">
    The draft Environment Bill sets out how we will maintain environmental standards as we leave the EU and build on the vision of the 25 Year Environment Plan.
  </p>

  </div>
</div>

